<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659826>
    dc:description "FIG. 180. Ivimka Creek in the Lakekamu River basin of Gulf Province, southern Papua New Guinea, CL 7149, habitat for R. aviavi n. sp. and R. ivimkana n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659830>
    dc:description "FIG. 187. A small headwater tributary to the Yaniwe River near Tekadu, Morobe Prov., southern Papua New Guinea, CL 7157a, type-locality for R. tekadu n. sp. and habitat for R. ivimkana n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659830/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659844>
    dc:description "FIGS. 209–211. Rhagovelia papuensis group, female ventral abdomen showing locations of depressions and patterns of setiferation. 209. Rhagovelia suloga n. sp.; specimen from Woodlark Is., Suloga Peninsula, CL 7217. 210. Rhagovelia ivimkana n. sp.; specimen from New Guinea, Tekadu, CL 7157. 211. Rhagovelia dinga n. sp.; specimen from New Guinea, Kamiali, CL 7243." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659844/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659872>
    dc:description "FIGS. 260–265. Rhagovelia ivimkana n. sp., structural details; specimens from New Guinea, Lakekamu River basin. 260. Wingless male, dorsal habitus; specimen from Sapoi River tributary, CL 7148. 261. Wingless female, dorsal habitus; specimen from Tekadu, CL 7157. 262. Male right hind leg, posterior view. 263. Male right hind leg, dorsal view; 262 and 263 from Sapoi River tributary, CL 7148. 264. Male left paramere, outer lateral view. 265. Male proctiger, dorsal view; 264 and 265 from Tekadu, CL 7157a." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659872/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659874>
    dc:description "FIG. 266. Distributions of species in the R. priori and R. transbintuni subgroups on eastern New Guinea and adjacent islands." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659874/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

